&quot;Here&#x27;s the thing. So, I had a garbage can to put my garbage bags into, but my grandpa fucking stole it because I took it down- I took my whole garbage can down to the trash people so they could pick up my trash, and he took my garbage can because he told me not to take my whole garbage can down there for whatever the fuck reason. So he took my garbage can, so I don&#x27;t have one anymore, and they have it outside their door. So, yeah, that fucking sucks. So I don&#x27;t really have anything or anywhere to put my fucking garbage bag, and they don&#x27;t give a fuck, and, um, it pisses me the fuck off, but what am I supposed to do, you know? So any fucking ways, um, I need somewhere to put the goddamn garbage from my house, and then I don&#x27;t want to fucking put it in my car to take it down to the fucking end of the road, like, because it&#x27;s nasty. It&#x27;s really fucking gross. I don&#x27;t want to do that, like...&quot;
&quot;Well, here&#x27;s the thing, dude. Like, I can&#x27;t fucking put garbage bags outside of my house because I live in the middle of the woods so the fucking animals tear it apart and then I have to clean up the fucking nasty-ass garbage from everywhere. And it&#x27;s just nasty. Like, I don&#x27;t know what the fuck to do. Like, I don&#x27;t have a... Like, it&#x27;s fucked up. It&#x27;s really fucked up.&quot;
&quot;No, I mean, I have a hundred bucks, but I&#x27;m supposed to use that for groceries, but fuck it. I feel like I can use it for whatever I want to fucking use it for, straight up. I need to get some shit to actually clean my house and stuff, you know, like, and fucking... Like, I need to get something to make my house not so grimy and nasty and maybe a goddamn garbage can.&quot;
&quot;I mean I already have a lot of cleaning stuff but I just feel like it&#x27;s not like I don&#x27;t know what the fuck is the problem but I feel like it&#x27;s just like it&#x27;s so much to literally have to clean like I don&#x27;t know what the fuck to do like maybe I need some cleaning tools or something really.&quot;
&quot;I mean, yeah, like, I need somewhere to put stuff, like, I don&#x27;t have anywhere to really put anything.&quot;
&quot;I don&#x27;t even know, like, there&#x27;s this one room that my mom used to live in, and so she moved out, right, but she had fucked up all the carpet shit, so I had to pull the carpet out, so it&#x27;s like bare baseboards in there, but my cat litter box is in there, and it&#x27;s disgusting, and there&#x27;s this old-ass couch in there that I can&#x27;t get out of there without my grandpa&#x27;s help, and I&#x27;m fucking, I moved it in there so I could get it out, but then what the fuck do I do with it, you know what I&#x27;m saying? I fucking hate it.&quot;
&quot;Maybe I would feel better if I got that shit taken care of. I don&#x27;t have a house anymore because my kids want a separate room.&quot;
&quot;I&#x27;d want it to be my kids&#x27; room. Like, they want separate rooms. I have my own room, but they share a room and they want separate rooms. And I need to clean it, but like, I don&#x27;t know how, because the paint&#x27;s fucked up. It looks fucked up. The ceiling fans took apart. I don&#x27;t fucking know. It&#x27;s just ugly and I hate it. And I don&#x27;t really have any way to really do anything about it.&quot;
